---
import Container from "../Container.astro"
---

<Container>
  <div class="pt-10 flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row items-center" id="hero">
    <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 py-4 sm:py-5 md:py-10 lg:py-20">
      <div class="text-left space-y-2 sm:space-y-3 md:space-y-4">
        <h1 class="mt-10 md:mt-0 text-[28px] font-semibold sm:text-[36px] md:text-[38px] lg:text-[40px] xl:text-[48px] leading-tight">
          Fai decollare il tuo business<br/>
          in 6 semplici passi con il <br/>“Metodo Storm X Digital”
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#F95C04] via-7% to-[#FF8E0A] to-82% text-white px-2 py-1 inline-block mt-2 rounded-lg">Come Un Collega</span>
        </h1>
          <!-- Hero image for small screens -->
        <div class="lg:hidden w-full h-full py-2 sm:py-12 md:py-12">
          <div class="relative w-full max-w-sm sm:max-w-md mx-auto">
            <img src="/hero_img.png" alt="Amazon Dashboard" class="w-full h-[400px] sm:h-[470px] object-cover" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mt-6 mb-4">
          Ti affianchiamo con call strategiche e tecniche nella gestione del tuo<br/>
          Amazon Seller e Vendor Central.  Avrai accesso a due meeting mensili <br/>
          dove potrai farci qualsiasi domanda e chiariremo qualsiasi tuo dubbio<br/> per il corretto funzionamento del tuo account Amazon.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4">
          <a 
            href="#"
            class="inline-block text-center w-full md:w-auto sm:px-24 md:px-9 py-3 sm:py-4 md:py-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#F95C04] via-7% to-[#FF8E0A] to-82% text-white font-bold text-base sm:text-lg rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl hover:bg-orange-700 transition duration-300"
          >
            CONTATTACI ORA
          </a>
          <div class="flex flex-col space-y-1 sm:space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <img src="/contatto.png" alt="Nessun Contratto Vincolante" class="w-4 sm:w-5 h-4 sm:h-5" />
              <span class="text-xs sm:text-sm">Consulenze Strategiche e Pratiche</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
              <img src="/approccio.png" alt="Approccio Su Misura" class="w-4 sm:w-5 h-4 sm:h-5" />
              <span class="text-xs sm:text-sm">Diventa un Esperto in Amazon Seller & Vendor</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center mt-6 sm:mt-8 space-x-3 sm:space-x-4">
        <img src="/amazon_ads.png" alt="Amazon Ads Verified Partner" class="h-16 sm:h-20 md:h-24 object-contain" />
        <img src="/amazon_spn.png" alt="Amazon SPN Certified" class="h-12 sm:h-14 md:h-16 object-contain" />
      </div>
    </div>
      <!-- Hero image for large screens -->
      <div class="hidden lg:flex w-full lg:w-1/2 py-12 sm:py-4 md:py-10 flex-col items-center lg:items-end">
        <div class="relative w-full max-w-sm sm:max-w-md">
          <img src="/hero_img.png" alt="Amazon Dashboard" class="w-full h-[616px] object-cover" />
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Collaborators Banner -->
  <div class="w-full py-6 sm:py-7 md:py-8 mt-8 sm:mt-9 md:mt-10">
    <div class="container">
      <img src="/collabs_banner.png" alt="Collaborators" class="w-full h-auto object-contain" />
    </div>
  </div>
</Container>